scramble a message

clone this project

copy the `config.json.sample` to `config.json`

    $ var Key = require('./key')

    $ var newKey = new Key();

    $ var secret = newKey.secret; // this is what you would give to someone so they could read your message

    $ var message = Key.sign('this is a message') // this will output a message

    $ var key2 = Key.FromSecret(secret)

    $ key2.decode(message) //=> returns 'this is a message'
